casebody.data:
Long LE, Ha Duong, and Emily Le
v.
WAKE MEDICAL CENTER, Michael Smith, Edgar Garrabrant, III, Cortney Sherev, Kendra Graham, S. Hantar, Brittany Johnson, Kathy Bryant, an Unknown Male Neonatalogist, and Unknown Female Triage Nurse. No. 457P03. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 5, 2004. Long Le, Pro Se. Ha Duong, Pro Se.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiffs on the 22nd day of August 2003 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th day of February 2004."

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiffs on the 22nd day of August 2003 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Wake County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th day of February 2004."
